{"tid":42081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中國讓位】為救人仔掟美債 美國最大債主由日本頂上","createTime":"2016-12-16T11:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T12:06:35.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7fff2bca6057a2dad64fa3095b3deb8d5b921a97","tid":42081,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:34:07.000Z","msg":"美國日前加息0.25厘，並預期未來加息步伐加快，美元持續強勢，人民幣貶值壓力大，今日繼續逼近「7算」水平。中國央行要動用外滙儲備托住人仔，而日本央行則樂見日圓貶值，一直是美國最大債主的中國要讓位日本了。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報道，美國周四公佈的外國對美國公債持有量數據顯示，中國的美債持有量減少413億美元，至1.115萬億美元，為逾六年來最低水平；並令中國截至10月，前12個月減持的美債總額達到1,392億美元，年度降幅是歷來第三大。儘管11月外匯儲備比2014年6月的高峰，減少了9,420億美元，降至3.052萬億美元的近六年低位，降幅達24%。但中國外匯儲備規模目前仍是全球最高。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述分析師稱，預計中國將持續減持美債以捍衛人民幣滙率，但看來不太可能進行大規模拋售。如果中國大舉賣出美債，可能會加大美國利率的上行壓力，反過來又會打壓人民幣匯率。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20161216/56056902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20161216%2F56056902&d=83lQcEWJoAF%2F9OIgYEsaK5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=a9bdbfba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20161216%2F56056902&h=c59325c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20161216/56056902</a>"},{"pid":"32c2b68531110dc194b86fff701ea607749a0095","tid":42081,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:36:43.000Z","msg":"橙，無得打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4eb054cddcbe68270e1f1bb85714e955c24fc8","tid":42081,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:41:35.000Z","msg":"要賣家當了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47a12dbf6599506eb94c6707de2735a86f5d9b8","tid":42081,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:46:27.000Z","msg":"賣美債，中國成最大贏家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n蠉蛷記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5271f787c84777d3104b428bc693413ccbaea8e","tid":42081,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:52:48.000Z","msg":"大量撤資外匯減少<br />\n唯有減持美債"},{"pid":"441e595d912ef0eb9b58ee2d546c4d918878121b","tid":42081,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:55:00.000Z","msg":"最大債主係美聯儲"},{"pid":"fa8174b24fa7325bcff2e3cd75d43c606afc6f71","tid":42081,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:55:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賣美債，中國成最大贏家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n蠉蛷記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買美債，中國成最大贏家"},{"pid":"43b552dda1416d162a7482fc0c93ac42d5a87395","tid":42081,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:06:35.000Z","msg":"即係掟又死唔掟又死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}